(firstQuint)CALM- 2 - Controlling and Lowering Blood Pressure With the MobiusHD.

 The objective of this study is to evaluate the safety and effectiveness of the MobiusHD System in a prospective, randomized, double-blind, sham-controlled multi-center pivotal study.

 Patients with resistant hypertension who remain uncontrolled despite pharmacologic treatment with maximum tolerated, guideline-directed anti-hypertensive pharmacologic therapy will be evaluated.

